{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"generalised-q-sampling-imaging\">\n<span id=\"gqi\"></span><h1>Generalised Q-Sampling Imaging<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#generalised-q-sampling-imaging\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>These notes are to help the user of the dipy module understand\nFrank Yeh&#8217;s Generalised Q-Sampling Imaging (GQI) [reference?].</p>\n<p>The starting point is the classical formulation of joint k-space\nand q-space imaging (Calaghan 8.3.1 p. 438) using the narrow\npulse gradient spin echo (PGSE) sequence of Tanner and Stejskal:</p>\n<div class=\"math\">\n<p><img src=\"../../_images/math/cf642c1dd13ff343d7c7080bff8ef448d404db6d.png\" alt=\"S(\\mathbf{k},\\mathbf{q}) = \\int \\rho(\\mathbf{r}) \\exp [j 2 \\pi\n\\mathbf{k} \\cdot \\mathbf{r}] \\int P_{\\Delta}\n(\\mathbf{r}|\\mathbf{r}',\\Delta) \\exp [j 2 \\pi \\mathbf{q} \\cdot\n(\\mathbf{r}-\\mathbf{r'})] \\operatorname{d}\\mathbf{r}'\n\\operatorname{d}\\mathbf{r}.\"/></p>\n</div><p>Here <img class=\"math\" src=\"../../_images/math/11a85f3c69ae6702cb1d99d3de451913b8f84c04.png\" alt=\"S\"/> is the (complex) RF signal measured at spatial wave number <img class=\"math\" src=\"../../_images/math/7b4de5ed98d4f86baba7a661e3a9eb2a274710f9.png\" alt=\"\\mathbf{k}\"/>\nand magnetic gradient wave number <img class=\"math\" src=\"../../_images/math/dd9f8e4fa6ad795780215243cbd5a5719b772ad3.png\" alt=\"\\mathbf{q}\"/>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"math\" src=\"../../_images/math/f574498915fa9e02eeb5141c24835d077eba3e75.png\" alt=\"\\rho\"/> is the local spin density (number of protons per unit volume\ncontributing to the RF signal).</p>\n<p><img class=\"math\" src=\"../../_images/math/296ab33356160c5a5d59477d3e898f58888f0bdb.png\" alt=\"\\Delta\"/> is the diffusion time scale of the sequence.</p>\n<p><img class=\"math\" src=\"../../_images/math/66c931efa8bca29d4d73c3801eece83a4209f91d.png\" alt=\"P_{\\Delta}\"/> is the averages diffusion propagator (transition\nprobability distribution).</p>\n</div>\n", "alabaster_version": "0.7.7", "display_toc": false, "title": "Generalised Q-Sampling Imaging", "sourcename": "theory/gqi.rst.txt", "customsidebar": null, "metatags": "", "current_page_name": "theory/gqi", "next": null, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Generalised Q-Sampling Imaging</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": null, "page_source_suffix": ".rst"}